---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Building at Work - may.labs" description="Product, AI, and navigating ambiguity in tech.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Building at work</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="content narrow">
    <p class="lead">
      How do you lead product teams when the cost of building drops to near-zero
      and the old playbooks stop working? How do you make decisions faster when
      certainty disappears?
    </p>

    <p>
      I lead AI-first transformation at a fintech with 15,000 people. This is
      where I'll share what I'm learning - about product, AI, ambiguity, and
      the decisions that shape how teams build.
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="insight-box">
      <span class="insight-label">Status</span>
      <p class="insight-text">I'm building this section. First pieces arriving soon.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/about" class="secondary-btn">More about me</a>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 5rem auto 3rem;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 0 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content > p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 3rem auto;
  }

  .insight-box {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(43, 74, 62, 0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .insight-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .insight-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .secondary-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.8rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }

  .secondary-btn:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--cream);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      margin: 3rem auto 2rem;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
